How To
GET FROM JFK
To MIDTOWN
WITHOUT EVER
TOUCHING THE
GROUND.
Now it is possible to travel between
New York's J.E.Kennedy Airport and
the 34th Street Heliport in midtown
Manhattan without fighting traffic.
New York Helicopter's regularly
scheduled service from American
Airlines Terminal 3, Gate 32 enables
you to rise above the aggravating
stop-and-go traffic below and arrive
at your midtown destinations calm
and relaxed, with time to spare. It's
a faster-than-ever way to get from
JFK to midtown and back, without
touching the ground.
Call Toll Free 1-800-645-3494
